===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 17 people, 13 households, and 10 families residing in the city. The [[population density]] was 77.0 inhabitants per square mile (29.7/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 17 housing units at an average density of 77.0 per square mile (29.7/km<sup>2</sup>). The median age was 62.5 years. 17.6% of residents were under the age of 18 and 47.1% were 65 years of age or older. For every 100 females, there were 41.7 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 40.0 males age 18 and over.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A15960&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A15960&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

The age distribution included 17.6% under the age of 20, 5.9% between the ages of 20 and 24, 5.9% from 25 to 44, and 23.5% from 45 to 64. The gender makeup of the city was 29.4% male and 70.6% female.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A15960&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

Of the 13 households, 46.2% had children under the age of 18 living in them. Of all households, 46.2% were [[Marriage|married-couple households]], 7.7% were cohabitating-couple households, 46.2% were households with a female householder and no spouse or partner present, and 0.0% were households with a male householder and no spouse or partner present. 23.1% of households were non-families, 23.1% were made up of individuals, and 7.7% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

Of the 17 housing units, 23.5% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 50.0%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

